The '''Hódmezővásárhely Wind Farm''' is an under construction wind power project in [[Csongrád County]], [[Hungary]]. It will have 14 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.wind-watch.org/news/2008/07/11/iberdrola-cleared-to-build-wind-farm-in-hodmezvasarhely-hungary/ Iberdrola cleared to build wind farm in Hódmezvásárhely, Hungary]</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 28 MW of power, enough to power over 11,077 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$45 million.

