'''Spectra Shield''' is a [[composite material]] (specifically, an [[ultra-high-molecular-weight polyethylene]] (UHMWPE) fiber) used in [[bulletproof vest]]s and [[vehicle armour]]. It is manufactured by [[Honeywell]].

Other popular fibers with similar uses are [[aramid]] ([[Kevlar]] or [[Twaron]]) and [[Dyneema]] (another UHMWPE).

